<BaseLayout>
  <div
    class="text-white w-full max-w-[800px] m-auto grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-4"
  >
    <a href="https://www.rpg-playbook.com" class="text-3xl">
      <h1 class="mb-6 flex flex-row justify-center">RPG Playbook</h1>
      <div
        class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between m-10 gap-10"
      >
        <img
          src="https://imagedelivery.net/eg6Xqa-jIrYvZBm8oCXnhg/5e23cc0f-d2cb-44da-f367-fdd1f2002b00/XLPortrait"
          alt="RPG Playbook Screenshot"
          class="max-h-[640px]"
        />
        <img
          src="https://imagedelivery.net/eg6Xqa-jIrYvZBm8oCXnhg/62bef899-32e9-45fa-a693-51adb213e500/XLPortrait"
          alt="RPG Playbook Screenshot"
          class="max-h-[640px]"
        />
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm md:text-base">
        RPG Playbook is an AI powered tool designed to enhance table-top RPG
        games. Using a combination of LLM and diffusion models, in conjunction
        with traditional software, the app allows users to create bespoke game
        assets in real time.
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-10 mb-6 flex flex-row justify-center text-xl">
        The Problem
      </h2>

      <p class="text-sm md:text-base mb-6">
        Tabletop RPG games are challenging to run. They require a significant
        creative input. A games master is expected to design a campaign, run all
        of the non-player characters, manage the upkeep for the mechanical side
        of play, and to respond and adjust in real time based on the player's
        choices.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm md:text-base mb-6">
        This is a daunting task even for a seasoned games master. Our aim with
        RPG Playbook is to make this much easier. We do this by lifting the
        creative burden from the games master. With just a few clicks the games
        master can gnerate new and exciting assets for their game, and do so in
        real time responding to the players specific choices within the
        narrative.
      </p>

