        real time responding to the players specific choices within the
        narrative.
      </p>

      <p class="text-sm md:text-base mb-6">
        These assets can also be pre-arranged into collections, and then used to
        create detailed and exciting campaigns. The AI aspect of the tool is
        highly flexible, and able to create a wide range of original assets for
        almost any kind of RPG game.
      </p>
    </a>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
